      <title>俄罗斯石油价格再次远高于七国集团的价格上限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/russian-oil-is-once-again-trading-far-above-the-g-7-s-price-cap-everywhere</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯石油的交易量远远超过了七国集团的价格上限，这本应剥夺莫斯科在乌克兰战争中的收入，这表明俄罗斯严重违反了该措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/russian-oil-is-once-again-trading-far-above-the-g-7-s-price-cap-everywhere</guid>
