    <item>
      <title>巴克莱银行的法律挑战风险使汽车金融调查复杂化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/barclays-legal-challenge-risks-complicating-motor-finance-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在巴克莱银行对英国金融投诉消费者监察员与此事相关的决定提出法律质疑后，金融行为监管局可能不得不扩大对汽车金融实践的长期调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/barclays-legal-challenge-risks-complicating-motor-finance-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 09:05:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民调显示祖马削弱非国大的支持，兰德暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/zar-usd-rand-plunges-as-poll-shows-support-for-anc-dropping-zuma-gains</link>
      <description><![CDATA[兰特从今年的最高水平下跌，此前一项新的民意调查显示，执政党非洲人国民大会的支持率大幅下降，前总统雅各布·祖马支持的政党可能成为该国第三大政党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/zar-usd-rand-plunges-as-poll-shows-support-for-anc-dropping-zuma-gains</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 08:35:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>津巴布韦的 ZiG 反映了银行努力转向黄金的涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/zimbabwe-s-zig-strengthens-for-second-day-gains-o-2-to-dollar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[津巴布韦的黄金支持货币 ZiG 自本周早些时候推出以来连续第二天走强，尽管该国所有银行尚未完全转向使用新单位。]]></description>
